title: 174 - The Billionaire Space Fight
description: Today’s episode features a full crew following the lead of Tony Digs. With Alarming news coming out today the boys jump right into the Pod FOD, which is a folder that is compiled from all things around the internet. Todays FOD leads off with the surprising news from “OnlyFans”, Two Billionaires engulfed in a space war, reactions to The Eternals television trailer, a Ric Flair look alike trending, and much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
